  "title": "Barista (Full Time / Part Time)",
  "description": "<p><strong>WE ARE HIRING – BARISTA CUM SERVICE CREW</strong></p><p><strong></strong><br /><strong>Employment Type:</strong> Full-time / Part-time</p><p><strong>✨ Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Prepare quality coffee, beverages, and café drinks</p></li><li><p>Provide friendly and efficient customer service</p></li><li><p>Take orders, serve food and maintain cleanliness of dining area</p></li><li><p>Operate POS system and handle daily transactions</p></li><li><p>Ensure proper hygiene, food safety and store cleanliness</p></li><li><p>Support daily café operations and assist teammates when needed</p></li></ul><p><strong>🔍 Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Prior barista experience is an advantage (training provided)</p></li><li><p>Good communication and positive working attitude</p></li><li><p>Able to work weekends, public holidays, and rotating shifts</p></li><li><p>Team player with a passion for F&B and customer service</p></li></ul><p><strong>💼 Benefits:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Staff meals provided</p></li><li><p>Uniform provided</p></li><li><p>Performance incentives</p></li><li><p>Career growth opportunities</p></li><li><p>Birthday Voucher </p></li></ul><p><strong>📩 How to Apply:</strong><br />Interested candidates, please WhatsApp / Email your resume to:<br />98895825</p><p><strong>Join us and be part of our café team! ☕</strong></p>",
